WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:41.000
Click '+' to add a new ACCOUNT.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:49.000
Enter the name of the new ACCOUNT.

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:02.000
Enter the amount of the balance on the ACCOUNT.

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:13.000
Select the date of the last payment.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:21.000
At this point, you must enter the payment methods available on ACCOUNT.

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:38.000
For example, the ATM, Credit Card, Checks, etc..

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:48.000
You can set a maximum monthly expense amount.

00:01:52.000 --> 00:02:00.000
You can select an icon to represent the payment.

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:10.000
Add, for example, a credit card.

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:35.000
Expenditure made with a credit card are charged the following month.

00:02:35.100 --> 00:02:43.000
Select the day of the month in which expenses will be charged.

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:18.000
In the case of checks is not necessary to set a maximum expenditure or a day of charge.

00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:36.000
The account has been created.

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:55.000
Now, when you insert a new transaction, you can select the new account and its payment methods.

